	CREATE TABLE onesdk1294.dbo.onesdk5596
	(
			//Define schema of table
			UserId          int, 
			Start           DateTime, 
			Region          string, 
			Query           string, 
			Duration        int, 
			Urls            string,

	);

	//create table weblogs on space-delimited website log data

	(

		s_sitename string,
		cs_method string, 
		cs_uristem string,
		cs_uriquery string,

		cs_bytes int,

			s_date DateTime,
			s_time string,
			s_sitename string,
			cs_method string,
			cs_uristem string,

	AS 
		SELECT * FROM 
		(
			VALUES(1,2),(2,4)
		) 
	AS 
	T(a, b);
	CREATE PROCEDURE onesdk1294.dbo.onesdk9010()
	AS BEGIN

		SELECT * FROM

	END;"

}
